		<h2>What is Eureka! Clinical Analytics?</h2>
        
		<p>Eureka! Clinical Analytics is a web application that provides you 
			with an easy way to phenotype a patient population based on their 
			clinical and administrative data, and load those phenotypes and 
			data into your own instance of the
			<a href="http://www.i2b2.org/">i2b2</a> data warehouse system. 
		</p>

		<p>Eureka! Clinical Analytics is developed and maintained by the
		<a href="http://cci.emory.edu">Emory Center for Comprehensive Informatics</a>.
		</p>

		<h2>Source Code</h2>
		<p>Source code for the current release (version ${currentStableVersion}) 
			is available from our 
			<a href="http://aiw.sourceforge.net">Sourceforge website</a>. You 
			can also download the 
			<a href="http://maven.cci.emory.edu/nexus/service/local/artifact/maven/redirect?r=aiw-snapshots&amp;g=edu.emory.cci.aiw.cvrg&amp;a=eureka&amp;v=LATEST&amp;c=src&amp;e=zip">latest snapshot</a> from our 
			<a href="http://maven.cci.emory.edu/nexus">Maven repository</a>.
		</p>

